                <div class="col-md-4"><figcaption><span class="title">Creative Brief.</span> <span class="caption-body">Document used to keep essential pieces of project and user context at the center of design discussions and meetings. Agreement on the content in the brief meant design work could progress in a focused way. This is a technique borrowed from Jared Spool's <a href="http://www.uie.com/articles/short_form_creative_brief/">User Interface Engineering web site</a>.</span></figcaption></div>
