        <p class="indent">I iterated from white board sketches and paper prototypes all the way to requirement and implementation. As design problems were tackled, the fidelity of our artifacts increased. First, the focus was on only a few key screens that users would interact with most. Our testing focused on these designs first. We would work out  detailed interactions and edge cases later.</p>

